games_dates = games.groupby('name')['year_of_release'].max()

.

In [26]:
def fill_dates(row):
    if pd.isnull(row['year_of_release']):
        name = row['name']
        return games_dates[name]
    else:
        return row['year_of_release']
In [27]:
games['year_of_release'] = games.apply(fill_dates, axis=1)
